'''Nerdgasm''' (also known as '''nerd-gasm''') is a [[neologism]] derived from the recent populatity of tendency seen in the sitcom ''[[Sex and the City]]'' to put the suffix "-gasm" with a word, place, or activity that is exciting, [[nerd]]s have placed the word "-gasm" with nerd. This word means something that would excite a [[nerd]], [[geek]], or [[Fan (aficionado)#Fanboy|fanboy]]. An example of this would be the announcing of a release date for a new [[video game console]], or a new scientific discovery.

